; Coverage test for filters.cc lines 1611-1616, 1638
; Tests payee_rewrite directive which triggers rewrite_posts filter.
; Line 1611: payee_rewrite_mappings iteration
; Line 1638: new payee assignment
; Each rewritten posting gets the new payee repeated since each creates
; a new temporary xact.

payee-rewrite Groceries  Whole Foods Market

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas              $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-15 Whole Foods Market    Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
24-Jan-15 Whole Foods Market    Assets:Cash                 $-50.00            0
24-Jan-20 Gas Station           Expenses:Gas                 $30.00       $30.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-30.00            0
end test
